{"tid":1391567,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【夢中香城online】戰爭的階段及簡易陣型形成方法","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T17:06:53.000Z","uid":264398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d3fc3a1668b0503c989bbb24c0c033968b37d205","tid":1391567,"uid":264398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"唔可避免，一場戰役隨著時間推移，我方愈有處於下風的可能，問題是我方如何適應及反制。<br />\n我應為我方可將戰爭推導以下個階段<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdRa99Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdRa99Q.jpg&h=89a0b3df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陣型可以很理想，但現實往往很難實行（e.g. 誰當領導？好盾難得）<br />\n但我認為 分區及 配合的意識是必須的，不要企鵝，不要落單。<br />\n（你可以不同意以下的圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGd5eC5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtGd5eC5.jpg&h=091602b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8fc7dfedbd2e1eb66bf8389eb4947ca24574ecd","tid":1391567,"uid":264398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"第2圖<br />\n和理非<br />\n&amp;*器材製成區"},{"pid":"e4733b448c9716c320d65442f0363dcf8ee9088c","tid":1391567,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"0483b8c6dd7fd0a1604c4432ae1a983fe4ae299e","tid":1391567,"uid":264398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"對方弱點分析<br />\n<br />\n防暴隊：<br />\n- 裝備重，移動較慢<br />\n我方可選擇游擊<br />\n<br />\n- 平時有固定陣式/武器<br />\n我方可以大概預計敵方的招數<br />\n敵方在個別地型亂戰可能失利<br />\n我方有進攻覺悟後(很難？)在游擊mode下可以嘗試前後夾擊<br />\n（假設對方只有一道防禦面）（成效未經驗證）<br />\n<br />\n- 個人利益<br />\n當受傷成本&gt;人工，有敵人會選擇後退<br />\n<br />\n速龍：<br />\n- 人數少<br />\n<br />\n水炮車：<br />\n- 無法應付分區式的游擊"},{"pid":"659ecf7cbf92075333aeed49d05f06a24f2138d8","tid":1391567,"uid":264398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:59:25.000Z","msg":"post 埋以前的分享<br />\n<br />\n流程的構想（沒包含分區式游擊）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMcxEmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMcxEmZ.jpg&h=d20b5f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vNRat5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vNRat5.jpg&h=5a127cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 陣地參考<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8SqeVP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8SqeVP.jpg&h=e96e0cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半陣地參考<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u60GxHz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu60GxHz.jpg&h=caf08841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全游擊沒有陣法<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fy38W9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFy38W9r.jpg&h=17954d0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf637ff53fab50283d3d749671a35105e4089dc5","tid":1391567,"uid":264398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:12:10.000Z","msg":"如果遮夠長e.g.711，可以係人與人之間刺擊（或用其他適當的工具）。<br />\n遮的手法可以參考以下<br />\n1：雙手用力刺<br />\n好處：大力d<br />\n壞處：無咁準<br />\n2：前手稍放後手刺<br />\n好處：準d<br />\n壞處：無咁大力<br />\n3：向下插，有人訓低時可用<br />\n4：劈<br />\n用柄唔係個傘頭<br />\n5：勾<br />\n腳，頸，持盾的手<br />\n注意難度大<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tkgnhcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftkgnhcd.jpg&h=e2508266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMQOXce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMQOXce.jpg&h=ef6b7a43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f9b6edbbf138562cf7d92d6e7dcc06b5c3852fa","tid":1391567,"uid":264398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5769635d1722656ceda9364b8b6433bac43536e1","tid":1391567,"uid":106480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSoQgnF.jpg\